  "detailed_description": "<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >BATTLE YOUR FRIENDS</h2><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1210880/extras/2c2da88a7346b9c31110faed43fa10d6.poster.avif?t=1660049164\" width=524 height=192 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1210880/extras/2c2da88a7346b9c31110faed43fa10d6.webm?t=1660049164\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1210880/extras/2c2da88a7346b9c31110faed43fa10d6.mp4?t=1660049164\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br>Dusk Warlocks is an online multiplayer <strong>spellcasting </strong>game in which up to 4 players compete in an unforgiving tactical battle. Learn how different spells work with one another and come up with <strong>cool spell combos</strong>. Your objective is to capture the energy crystal before other players kill you or kill the player that is currently trying to capture it.<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >BUILD YOUR SPELL ARSENAL</h2><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1210880/extras/22dbd107d2539c3511c18ee323b00edf.poster.avif?t=1660049164\" width=524 height=192 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1210880/extras/22dbd107d2539c3511c18ee323b00edf.webm?t=1660049164\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1210880/extras/22dbd107d2539c3511c18ee323b00edf.mp4?t=1660049164\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br>The spells you use, that's completely up to you! Spells are categorized into <strong>7 elements: Fire, Water, Ice, Air, Stone, Wood and Electricity</strong>. Every element has many spells to choose from, which makes the possible combinations almost endless. Pick out the 3 elements you want to fight with and equip 2 spells to each.<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >CREATE YOUR WARLOCK</h2><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1210880/extras/0fbad3bf10c277773cbae671351ce979.poster.avif?t=1660049164\" width=524 height=192 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1210880/extras/0fbad3bf10c277773cbae671351ce979.webm?t=1660049164\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1210880/extras/0fbad3bf10c277773cbae671351ce979.mp4?t=1660049164\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br>Dusk Warlocks features <strong>30+ different characters</strong> as well as <strong>thousands of unique spell combinations </strong>that allow you to make your Warlock feel unique and personalized.",
  "about_the_game": "<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >BATTLE YOUR FRIENDS</h2><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1210880/extras/2c2da88a7346b9c31110faed43fa10d6.poster.avif?t=1660049164\" width=524 height=192 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1210880/extras/2c2da88a7346b9c31110faed43fa10d6.webm?t=1660049164\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1210880/extras/2c2da88a7346b9c31110faed43fa10d6.mp4?t=1660049164\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br>Dusk Warlocks is an online multiplayer <strong>spellcasting </strong>game in which up to 4 players compete in an unforgiving tactical battle. Learn how different spells work with one another and come up with <strong>cool spell combos</strong>. Your objective is to capture the energy crystal before other players kill you or kill the player that is currently trying to capture it.<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >BUILD YOUR SPELL ARSENAL</h2><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1210880/extras/22dbd107d2539c3511c18ee323b00edf.poster.avif?t=1660049164\" width=524 height=192 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1210880/extras/22dbd107d2539c3511c18ee323b00edf.webm?t=1660049164\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1210880/extras/22dbd107d2539c3511c18ee323b00edf.mp4?t=1660049164\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br>The spells you use, that's completely up to you! Spells are categorized into <strong>7 elements: Fire, Water, Ice, Air, Stone, Wood and Electricity</strong>. Every element has many spells to choose from, which makes the possible combinations almost endless. Pick out the 3 elements you want to fight with and equip 2 spells to each.<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >CREATE YOUR WARLOCK</h2><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1210880/extras/0fbad3bf10c277773cbae671351ce979.poster.avif?t=1660049164\" width=524 height=192 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1210880/extras/0fbad3bf10c277773cbae671351ce979.webm?t=1660049164\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1210880/extras/0fbad3bf10c277773cbae671351ce979.mp4?t=1660049164\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br>Dusk Warlocks features <strong>30+ different characters</strong> as well as <strong>thousands of unique spell combinations </strong>that allow you to make your Warlock feel unique and personalized.",
